{"tid":188871,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[希望有人知] 跪尋1款PC即時戰略 98-2000年到","createTime":"2017-04-06T04:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T07:28:11.000Z","uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a51f822d71d485f6e6bfde6227c3622357ca7b77","tid":188871,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"果時小學雞 玩過隻即時戰略好正 希望有人玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係即時戰略 分左3個國家好似<br />\n<br />\n時代係古羅馬?<br />\n<br />\n因為士兵衣著係羅馬定希臘, 而其中一個國係全白色帽/衫 拎錘既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有兩個位特別記得 <br />\n<br />\n1)有得生產車<br />\n<br />\n其中1款係有得渣既投石車, 係要搵個士兵上去坐 先可以郁到 , 如果俾人打死左個士兵 架車就唔會再郁到<br />\n<br />\n2)有得起陷阱 , 個陷阱係假平地,底係好多木樁 ,無論自己定敵人行過就會死<br />\n<br />\n希望有人知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #我係1998- 2000年咁上下玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4478bdba0c9951957017c7c8b10b541ef42d55a9","tid":188871,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"畫面/畫風似aoc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19072bed9433c100cdb2e459d7ec39c5d0e9a1f","tid":188871,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"Rise of nations?"},{"pid":"1cb94c917b31d39a4e59d954765db5f80accb125","tid":188871,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"定age of empires"},{"pid":"7b41f9472d5b254d34e2224b08ebd73d494c688c","tid":188871,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定age of empires</blockquote><br />\n一定唔係世紀帝國<br />\n<br />\n但印像中畫風好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa3932227548e8f657d8c0df913546efa2d3ac7","tid":188871,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB